<p>
<lb n="1"/>bu sēsi ḍi <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> guḍlu prākāraṁbu maṁṭa<unclear>pa</unclear>ṁbunu namayiṁcina 
<lb n="2"/>sa<unclear>ṁ</unclear>pannuṇḍu <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> maya bejeyarāju bejeyēśvara<unclear>ṁ</unclear>bu galasi sarvva <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>śvarapakṣapāti dēvabrāhmaṇaguru<unclear>bha</unclear>ktiparuṇḍu sakti<unclear>tra</unclear>ya 
<lb n="4"/>sā <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> samastarājyā <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> ranirūpitamahāmantrādhipati 
<lb n="5"/>dhāri <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> bejeyarāju samarttu ṇḍani Ā <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> nmata <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> na bancina <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>(ṁ)mma <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> dyōgammuna <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> bṛhaspatisamānu layna pergeḍa<unclear>kā</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/>paṇḍaraṁgunu Ayyamape<unclear>gga</unclear>ḍalu garanammuna paṇḍaraṁgu <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> rā <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="8"/>[A]yyapayyaya sakaḷaśāstrārttapāragu layna 
<lb n="9"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> nikēśvaruna<unclear>kuṁ</unclear> gārttikēyuṇḍubōle <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> lavināśavi <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="10"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> bhramarō <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> śrīmatkaḍeyarāju guṇagaṇābharaṇuṇḍu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<p>Note.—This inscription seems to be in Telugu verse but, in its present incomplete form, the verses cannot be reconstructed.</p>

<p>This record is published in <hi rend="italic">Nellore Inscriptions,</hi> p. 968, but the reading there is incorrect in places.</p>

